{"tid":1973014,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯合國秘書長古特雷斯: 現時並未是時候向世衛減少資源","createTime":"2020-04-15T02:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T11:13:06.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":210,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"03690801e578c254a16d206065295f710420f514","tid":1973014,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T02:06:17.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普宣布，停止向世界衛生組織撥款。聯合國秘書長古特雷斯表示，現時並未是時候向世衛或其他應對武漢肺炎疫情的人道組織減少資源。<br />\n<br />\n古特雷斯表示，世界必須支持世衛的工作，對戰勝疫情至關重要。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮記者會上指出，世衛在武漢肺炎疫情爆發時，未有履行基本職責，發布中國對病毒的虛假信息，令疫情爆發的範圍比原本更大，他正要求審視評估世衛管控失誤及隱瞞疫情散播的情況。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1520669_1_20200415094248.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1520669_1_20200415094248.jpg&h=604c23ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520669-20200415.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520669-20200415.htm&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=4bd4bb45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520669-20200415.htm&h=5c6f2eda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520669-20200415.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2627a5be3cc42122a713fc6dad05b91a1142f0a6","tid":1973014,"uid":140967,"like":106,"dislike":1,"score":105,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T02:08:02.000Z","msg":"聯合國呢位又收左中共幾多錢<br />\n<br />\n美國一定要查下"},{"pid":"8ab3de96f7f34791191b26d512009ade4ddc2347","tid":1973014,"uid":61395,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T02:08:52.000Z","msg":"唔係應該叫唔好減budget 反而叫人遲d先減<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec552d48f96ff41b5eac29a23513bbea38762284","tid":1973014,"uid":284855,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime